.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5901bcddcd08dbf546a3170a90ad4956623658","tid":553173,"uid":144692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84573d3e7f560597e38775ce1db35da3eec64780","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f23255b9cbff01c3db23af5201fe624849dfe94d","tid":553173,"uid":144692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T13:12:58.000Z","msg":"邊間醫院做？<br />\n如果公立醫院，等左幾耐<br />\n<br />\n我仲等緊箍牙 9月份去醫院複診睇下d骨生曬味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T14:43:58.000Z","msg":"上面有寫<br />\n我自己就屯門醫院做 6個月<br />\n聯合 2年<br />\nqe/瑪麗就應該一年至年半<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:17:14.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇tg?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知更多手術既野,thx!"},{"pid":"3955ba9ca2b5088d16776bf4a0f19154c751af2f","tid":553173,"uid":13796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我細個開始箍，因為上下顎既牙都唔齊&quot;當時大約小五六開始青少年發育階段&quot; <br />\n箍齊左之後個牙醫叔叔話我開始有倒及牙既問題，就開始落橡筋箍，最後都阻止唔到，而家牙顎上顎唔齊。<br />\n下顎凸出0.5CM 左右， 醫生話唔過份，唔影響生活就唔建議做手術，咁雙親就話唔好做啦咁就冇做。<br />\n<br />\n最大影響就係...下唇好易乾燥甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9e69a1150969267f4bbbaeaeaa24a70ae3ad73","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4901f91dcfa892a342efa2fac68cd195cdc15d83","tid":553173,"uid":89252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84573d3e7f560597e38775ce1db35da3eec64780","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f23255b9cbff01c3db23af5201fe624849dfe94d","tid":553173,"uid":144692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-0