AAAAAA6LMUyhgVdKSwMwpg&d=y%2Bec4sQHKQqngYfow8DPRLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=fca27c9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAA6LMUyhgVdKSwMwpg</a><br />\n其實有正顎tg gp<br />\n有做左多年/未做/台灣/私家/公立既巴絲打<br />\n大家可以入去問下問題咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1690a6048c7589eae46dfb1ea151c20bdebf93","tid":553173,"uid":34222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:00:03.000Z","msg":"做完半年<br />\n<br />\n係開頭兩個月最辛苦<br />\n<br />\n而家下巴感覺冇以前咁敏感<br />\n<br />\n但中線對齊哂<br />\n<br />\n係菲臘做 做完醫生話效果幾好"},{"pid":"684969b094ed2d709ef1cdb2ba0bfde80ab70557","tid":553173,"uid":85439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"諗住排菲臘教學症 有咩要注意"},{"pid":"5279ccff1432c6ee612019bf504f684b0d014cbe","tid":553173,"uid":151575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58bc469a117e029b7a78cb82fb8972152020014","tid":553173,"uid":151575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"684969b094ed2d709ef1cdb2ba0bfde80ab70557","tid":553173,"uid":85439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"諗住排菲臘教學症 有咩要注意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e114312f155766c53697358619defb53a686053","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"684969b094ed2d709ef1cdb2ba0bfde80ab70557","tid":553173,"uid":85439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"諗住排菲臘教學症 有咩要注意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:54:18.000Z","msg":"打去問下呢個時期收唔收症比較好<br />\n如果收就啦啦聲搵個專科箍牙轉介你去<br />\n因為菲臘時收時唔收的 miss左又唔等幾時再收"},{"pid":"4f672395ecce953ce82b6ee8f5e242c87e89af1c","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5279ccff1432c6ee612019bf504f684b0d014cbe","tid":553173,"uid":151575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T00:04:26.000Z","msg":"係香港做既過箍術前術後都要箍牙<br />\n箍齊左上下排先會俾你排手術期<br />\n因為咁樣度出黎個手術plan會好過你做左手術先<br />\n咁術後顎骨位置變左可能啲牙會變翻有少少對唔正<br />\n所以術後都係要繼續箍的<br />\n不過聽其他人講都係好多都好快就拆得翻箍<br />\n<br />\n做左手術先就可能做完出黎<br />\n箍翻齊啲牙個陣啲牙對唔到太正既位<br />\n<br />\n台灣就通常手術先 不過人地技術成熟少少<br />\n包埋少少整容成份 會幫你修埋腮骨<br />\n<br />\n剝牙呢個要睇你啲牙同骨既情況<br />\n醫生會同箍牙醫生開會傾點幫你最好<br />\n智慧齒既話通常會幫你剝埋<br />\n我既話就剝左2隻未出智慧齒2隻臼齒"},{"pid":"bf6243ed4bd676b2714cd9f6e3d4b800bee2d369","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f9786328e9bc0310ab6ab31154433b43fe6529","tid":553173,"uid":89252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58bc469a117e029b7a78cb82fb8972152020014","tid":553173,"uid":151575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"684969b094ed2d709ef1cdb2ba0bfde80ab70557","tid":553173,"uid":85439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:07:02.000Z","msg":"諗住排菲臘教學症 有咩要注意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"箍牙教學病人佢地呢排唔係收手術case所以唔收<br />\n無謂嘥50蚊仲要俾人評頭品足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另一個原因係佢地希望啲教學病人可以三年內完左個case<br />\n呢點對需要做手術嘅病人都幾難"},{"pid":"9ce5e7c4afe0c53c19bf4668493953a6a85da719","tid":553173,"uid":70877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4cc69c1b47e6e30609c1ee8f3c4138b12c7ee09","tid":553173,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"小學到form2時整左<br />\n佢裝舊野撐大個上顎<br />\n再要每晚戴舊野頂住頭頂同下巴<br />\n禁返下顎入去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/