},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"唔係箍左牙先<br />\n係要去左睇箍牙醫生先 箍牙醫生睇完會轉介你去醫院<br />\n之後等醫院收症同開大會 決定好手術方向先箍牙<br />\n<br />\n至於箍牙醫生方面比較聽得多人去睇既有<br />\n趙創波<br />\n岑儉(想睇佢既 要每月既一號打去預約 一個月入面剩係得呢一日收症)<br />\n不過都要睇你想排邊間醫院<br />\n唔同醫生合作開既醫院都唔同"},{"pid":"167bb4275fa012b616420041a5bc6c2729289ae4","tid":553173,"uid":171958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"雖然我冇做呢個手術，不過入到黎都想問下關於箍牙既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇邊間箍牙比較平同好<br />\n箍牙有冇咩要留意既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487c648f7c8165c77e35cb28436538d6f3de5460","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"167bb4275fa012b616420041a5bc6c2729289ae4","tid":553173,"uid":171958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:04:31.000Z","msg":"雖然我冇做呢個手術，不過入到黎都想問下關於箍牙既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇邊間箍牙比較平同好<br />\n箍牙有冇咩要留意既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"你唔大問題既話去普通牙科醫生箍就最平<br />\n好既話個個感覺都唔同 最好自己去consult多幾間感受下<br />\n<br />\n注意既事頂其實都無咩<br />\n係開頭箍第1個月會痛少少之外 之後就唔會再痛<br />\n可以揀下想箍隱適美/鐵箍(陶瓷/鐵粒)咁"},{"pid":"fa2c167008652ad60201c480a9b219cfa6f02a66","tid":553173,"uid":53089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cecfc8bb29df83c0cdc721a880b1380c3a807694","tid":553173,"uid":1491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d5464e017663a75866a42adde76d64fae5e19d4","tid":553173,"uid":53089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:52:32.000Z","msg":"係咪要箍咗牙先有轉介信去公立醫院排期？<br />\n有冇箍牙醫生推薦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma